{"article_id":"B2PE2qei0XqDCIcN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The AirAsia jet","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"carrying 162 passengers","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that disappeared over 24 hours ago","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"is suspected to be on the bottom of the ocean floor ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Indonesia 's top rescue officials said at a press conference Monday .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"`` Based on the coordinates","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that we know ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"the evaluation would be","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that any estimated crash position is in the sea ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"and that the hypothesis is the plane is at the bottom of the sea , ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"National Search and Rescue chief Henry Bambang Soelistyo told a news conference ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"according to the Associated Press .","depth":4},{"id":12,"text":"First Admiral Sigit Setiayana , the Naval Aviation Center commander at the Surabaya air force base , told the Associated Press","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"that 12 navy ships , five planes , three helicopters and a number of warships were talking part , along with ships and planes from Singapore and Malaysia .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"The Australian Air Force also sent a search plane .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Setiayana said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"visibility was good .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"`` God willing ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"we can find it soon , ''","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"he told The Associated Press .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Malaysia and Singapore each planned to deploy one C-130 plane and three ships .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Australia will also help ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"he added .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"William Waldock , an expert on air crash search and rescue with Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University in Prescott , Arizona , cautioned","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"against drawing comparisons to Flight 370 .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"The circumstances bode well","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"for finding Flight 8501","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"since the intended flight time was less than two hours ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and there is a known position","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"where the plane disappeared ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"he told the Associated Press .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"A groom-to-be , his parents and three brothers are believed to be among those aboard an Air Asia jet","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"carrying 162 people","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"that vanished over the Java Sea early Sunday amid stormy weather .","depth":4},{"id":34,"text":"The fiancé of Alain Oktavianus Siaun told reporters","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"that she was trying to stay positive","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"after hearing the news","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"that AirAsia Flight 8501 had disappeared en route to Singapore ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"the Star in Malaysia reported Sunday .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"\" I heard it on the radio","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"and immediately browsed the Internet","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and saw the news , \"","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"Louise Sidharta said ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"according to told the newspaper .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" My heart knew by then","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that my fiancé was on that flight . \"","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Siaun was heading to Singapore","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"to vacation with his family for the last time as a bachelor .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Sidharta took a later flight from Surabaya to Singapore .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"She spoke to a horde of reporters at the Singapore Changi International Airport .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"\" We have to stay positive","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"and hope","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that they","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"( loved ones )","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"could be found soon , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"AirAsia said","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"there are 155 passengers on board-138 adults , 16 , children and one infant .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Also on board are two pilots and five crew members .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"The Associated Press said","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"dozens of relatives of people aboard the plane gathered in a room at the Surabaya airport","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"to await word about their loved ones .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Sky News said","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"a British businessman and his two-year-old daughter are believed to be on the flight .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Most on board are from Indonesia , with three from South Korea and one each from Singapore , Malaysia , France and the United Kingdom .","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"Indonesia and Singapore have launched a search and rescue operation","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"after the flight was reported missing .","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"Flight 8501 was scheduled to make a relatively short early-morning flight from Surabaya , Indonesia to Singapore ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"but lost contact with Jakarta air traffic control at 6:24 a.m. local time","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"( 6:24 p.m. Eastern Time Saturday ) ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"approximately an hour before it was due to land .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Eleven minutes earlier ,","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"according to Djoko Murjatmodjo , Indonesia 's acting director general of transportation ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"the pilot had `` asked to hinder cloud","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"by turning left","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and go higher to 34,000 feet . ''","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Murjatmodjo said","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"that there was no distress signal from the plane .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"AirAsia Indonesia had earlier confirmed","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"that the pilot had asked to change course","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"due to bad weather in the area .","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"`` We hope","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"we can find the location of the plane as soon as possible ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"and we hope","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"that God will give us guidance","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"to find it , ''","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"Murjatmodjo told reporters .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"`` We do n't dare to presume","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"what has happened","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"except that it has lost contact . \"","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"Flight 8501 was last seen on radar at 6:16 a.m. ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"and a minute later was no longer there ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"he added .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"`` This is my worst nightmare , ''","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"AirAsia founder Tony Fernandes said in a tweet .","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"Earlier , Fernandes , the face of the company and an active Twitter user , sent out a tweet","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that said :","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"`` Thank you for all your thoughts and prays","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"[ sic ] .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"We must stay strong . ''","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Sunardi , a weather forecaster at the Indonesia 's Meteorology and Geophysics Agency","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"who uses only one name ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"told the Associated Press","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that dense storm clouds were detected up to 44,000 feet in the same area at the time","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"the plane was reported to have lost contact .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"`` There could have been turbulence , lightning and vertical as well as horizontal strong winds within such clouds , ''","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"AirAsia said","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"the single-aisle Airbus A320-200 had an Indonesian captain and a French co-pilot .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"The airline 's statement added","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"that the plane 's captain had a total of 6,100 flying hours ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"while the first officer had flown 2,275 hours .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Flightradar24 , a flight tracking website , said","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"the plane was delivered in September 2008 ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"which would make it six years old .","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"It said","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"the plane was flying at 32,000 feet , the regular cruising altitude for most jetliners ,","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"when the signal from the plane was lost .","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"AirAsia said","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that the plane had undergone its last scheduled maintenance on Nov. 16 .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Murjatmodjo , the Indonesian official , said","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"the plane is believed to have vanished somewhere over the Java Sea between Tanjung Pandan on Belitung island and Pontianak , on Indonesia 's part of Kalimantan island .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Transport Minister Ignasius Jonan told reporters in Surabaya","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"that the position was believed to be near the coast line .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"search and rescue efforts now involved the Indonesian army , the national Search and Rescue Agency as well as Singapore and Malaysia .","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"The Search and Rescue Agency 's operation chief , Maj. Gen. Tatang Zaenudin , said","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"200 rescuers had been deployed to the east side of Belitung island .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Air Force spokesman Hadi Tjahjanto said","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"three aircraft ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"including a surveillance plane ,","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"had been dispatched to the area .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"The Singapore air force and the navy also were searching with two C-130 planes .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"The Singapore aviation authority said","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"it was informed about the missing plane by Jakarta ground control","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"about half an hour after the contact was lost .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Malaysian Prime Minister Najib Razak , expressed solidarity with AirAsia .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"In a tweet he said :","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"`` Very sad to hear","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"that AirAsia Indonesia QZ8501 is missing .","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"My thoughts are with the families .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Malaysia stands ready to help . ''","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"White House spokesman Eric Schultz said in a statement","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that President Obama had briefed about the missing flight","depth":9},{"id":144,"text":"and officials would continue to monitor the situation .","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"According to the website FlightAware.com ,","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"Flight QZ8501 was scheduled to depart from Juanda International Airport , near Surabaya on the Indonesian island of East Java at 5:30 a.m. local time ,","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"with arrival in Singapore scheduled for 8:20 a.m. Singapore time","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"( 7:20 p.m. Eastern Time Saturday ) .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"It had last flown the route on Dec. 26 .","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"The Airbus A320 is a workhorse of modern aviation .","depth":6},{"id":151,"text":"Similar to the Boeing 737 , it is used","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"to connect cities anywhere from one to five hours apart .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"There are currently 3,606 A320s in operation worldwide ,","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"according to Airbus .","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"The A320 family of jets ,","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"which includes A319 and A321 ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"has a very good safety record , with just 0.14 fatal accidents per million takeoffs ,","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"according to a safety study","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"published by Boeing in August .","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"AirAsia ,","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"which has a presence in several Southeast Asian countries ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"has never lost a plane before .","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"AirAsia Malaysia owns 49 percent of the Indonesian subsidiary .","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"The airline typically flies short routes of just a few hours ,","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"connecting large cities of Southeast Asia .","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"However , recently it has tried to expand into long-distance flying through its sister airline AirAsia X .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"Earlier this year , national carrier Malaysia Airlines lost two planes .","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"Flight MH370 vanished on March 8 with 239 passengers and crew on board .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"On July 17 , Flight MH17 was shot down over Ukraine ,","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"killing all 298 people on board .","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"William Waldock , an expert on air crash search and rescue with Embry-Riddle Aeronautical University in Prescott , Arizona , cautioned","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"against drawing comparisons to the disappearance of Malaysia Airlines Flight 370 .","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"`` I think","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"we have to let this play out , ''","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"`` Hopefully , the airplane will get found ,","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"and","depth":14},{"id":178,"text":"if that happens ,","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"it will probably be in the next few hours .","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"Until then , we have to reserve judgment . ''","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"The circumstances bode well","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"for finding the plane","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"since the intended flight time was less than two hours","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"and there is a known position","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"at which the plane disappeared ,","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"he said .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":373,"left":217,"right":372,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":198,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":191,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":190,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":190,"left":189,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":196,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":195,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":192,"right":194,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":194,"left":7,"right":193,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":193,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":216,"left":208,"right":215,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":205,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":199,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":14,"right":203,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":200,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":201,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pa